.DT
remove_hide_invis
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
remove_hide_invis

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
remove_hide_invis -  This method removed the hiding of the specified type off the object.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
varargs int remove_hide_invis(string type,
int quiet)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^type%^RESET%^ - the type of hiding to remove
%^BOLD%^quiet%^RESET%^ - flag to pass along to the callback function
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 on success, 0 on failure

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/basic/hide_invis.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method removed the hiding of the specified type off the object.
This method will call the function setup when the hiding was added
when the hiding is removed. If you pass 1 as the second argument, it
will send the 'quiet' flag to the callback function.
.EP

